title: Oh, baby! Carole Samaha to share first photos of her newborn girl in an original way
text:

Published October 21st, 2015 - 12:05   Carole Samaha will finally share photos of her newborn baby in an adorable and unique way. (File photo) Follow > Click here to add Carole Samaha as an alert Click here to remove the Carole Samaha alert Disable alert for Carole Samaha , Click here to add Facebook as an alert Click here to remove the Facebook alert Disable alert for Facebook Click here to add Walid Mustafa as an alert Click here to remove the Walid Mustafa alert Disable alert for Walid Mustafa 
We've only got to hold our breaths a little longer before we finally get to see what Carole Samaha's newborn baby looks like. 
The Lebanese singer's press office announced that a new single dedicated to baby Tala will soon be released... and there's more! 
New mama Carole will not only be singing for her little bundle of joy, but she will release the first photos of Tala in the music video as well. Such a unique way to introduce Tala to the world. 
Photo: Facebook. 
Miss Samaha gave birth to a healthy girl after announcing her surprise pregnancy back in May. 
She announced the news on her Facebook page in August by posting this very pink pic along with the caption, " Welcome to the world our precious Angel #TALA 31.8.2015." 
Photo: Facebook. 
Will Tala look more like her 43-year-old celebrity mama, or her Egyptian businessman papa Walid Mustafa ?
